spx.packets

Class AlertLogicRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.AlertLogicRegion

  • public class AlertLogicRegion
extends java.lang.Object
    AlertLogicRegion

    The AlertLogicRegion structure is used to report region information within AlertLogic structures.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketAlertLogicRegion structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    AlertLogic
